name: Stack of Stretchy Picasso Glass Bead Bracelets
description:
This stack of fancy beaded bracelets will fit an average size woman's wrist (6 1/2 to 7 1/4 inch). 

Six gorgeous bracelets composed of picasso, aged, shiny and matte glass seed beads in sizes from 10/0 to 1/0 (2.2-7mm in diameter). 

Many different shapes, sizes and facets add to a natural bohemian look!

Wear one or as many as you want!  

You will receive the exact group of pieces pictured.
